  <TR><TD BGCOLOR="#add8ff" WIDTH="150"><B>Analysis</B></TD></TR>
  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">Since the Roses owned all the stock of<BR ALIGN='left'/>both the transferor and transferee<BR ALIGN='left'/>corporations we hold that no<BR ALIGN='left'/>distribution of stock or securities was<BR ALIGN='left'/>necessary to meet the requirements of §<BR ALIGN='left'/>368(a)(1)(D).</TD></TR>
