<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLBORDER="1" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="4">
  <TR><TD BGCOLOR="#b6e3b6" WIDTH="150"><B>Rule</B></TD></TR>
  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">Section 354(a)(1) provides that &quot;[n]o<BR ALIGN='left'/>gain or loss shall be recognized if<BR ALIGN='left'/>stock or securities in a corporation a<BR ALIGN='left'/>party to a reorganization are, in<BR ALIGN='left'/>pursuance of the plan of reorganization,<BR ALIGN='left'/>exchanged solely for stock or securities<BR ALIGN='left'/>in such corporation or in another<BR ALIGN='left'/>corporation a party to the<BR ALIGN='left'/>reorganization.&quot;[7]\n\nHowever, §<BR ALIGN='left'/>354(b)(1) limits the application of §<BR ALIGN='left'/>354(a)(1) by requiring<BR ALIGN='left'/>that:\n\nSubsection (a) shall not apply<BR ALIGN='left'/>to an exchange in pursuance of a plan of<BR ALIGN='left'/>reorganization within the meaning of<BR ALIGN='left'/>section 368(a)(1)(D), unless —\n(A) the<BR ALIGN='left'/>corporation to which the assets are<BR ALIGN='left'/>transferred acquires substantially all<BR ALIGN='left'/>of the assets of the transferor of such<BR ALIGN='left'/>assets. (Emphasis added.)</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
>]
	"5p0vJ2KyNd" [label=<
