  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">&quot;substantially all&quot; requirement is<BR ALIGN='left'/>determined by focusing on the transfer<BR ALIGN='left'/>of the operating assets by the<BR ALIGN='left'/>transferor and not on the non-operating<BR ALIGN='left'/>or liquid assets such as cash.</TD></TR>
